lanta bronx brooklyn chicago cleveland dallas denver detroit houston las vegas los angeles miami minneapolis new york philadelphia phoenix saint louis san antonio san diego san jose   chamberofcommercecom capriottis  wikipedia capriottis from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search capriottis logo type private industry fast casual founded wilmington delaware us  founder lois and alan margolet number of locations  key people ashley morris ceo jason smylie cio george chanos chairman products sandwiches subs soups other food products website capriottiscom capriottis is a las vegasbased fast casual restaurant chain located in the united states the restaurant chain was founded in wilmington delaware in  capriottis has  companyowned and franchise locations in  states including the district of columbia contents  history  business operations  products  technology  references  external links historyedit capriottis was founded in wilmington delaware in  the restaurant is named after the founders grandfather philip capriotti in  the second restaurant location opened in new castle delaware in  capriottis began franchising their restaurants in  the first restaurant location in las vegas nevada was opened on sahara avenue near las vegas boulevard in  ashley morris and jason smylie opened a franchise in las vegas at the time morris was the youngest financial adviser at wells fargo smylie was a software engineer at bechtel nevada morris and smylie were also investors in the housing market and made the decision to invest in a franchise after learning that the return on investment was higher than anything they were looking at investing in in  morris and smylie put the company in escrow in the following year morris smylie and a group of investors consisting of  las vegans bought capriottis capriottis had  restaurant locations by the end of  morris is the ceo of the company in  and  the chain was the official sandwich sponsor of the world series of poker in las vegas capriottis was ranked in entrepreneur magazines top  franchise list in  and remained ranked through  capriottis starred on food networks unwrapped in december  in november  capriottis expanded its presence on the east coast by opening its first location in washington dc joe biden was the first customer served at the stores grand opening that year capriottis brought in over  million in revenue and experienced a  growth over the previous three years in  the company was named one of the top  best food franchises for your buck and one of americas best franchises by forbes magazine the sandelman  associates quick track study on the top  quick service restaurant concepts ranked capriottis among the top ten in overall satisfaction and won the award for highest quality and taste in the  study business operationsedit capriottis is based in las vegas nevada and has its largest concentration of shops there the restaurant chain has  locations in  states including arizona california delaware florida illinois iowa maryland massachusetts nebraska nevada north carolina pennsylvania texas utah washington state wisconsin and washington dc in  it ranked  in entrepreneurs franchise  in  capriottis was ranked  in entrepreneurs franchise  productsedit capriottis specializes in cold grilled and vegetarian submarine sandwiches each restaurant roasts whole turkeys for  hours nightly hand pulls meats and makes their own meatballs and coleslaw in november  the bobbie one of capriottis signature sandwiches was voted the greatest sandwich in america by aolcom the sandwich is made with pulled turkey cranberry sauce stuffing and mayonnaise the margolets named it after their aunt in  usa today named capriottis one of the  great places for a surprising sandwich technologyedit capriotti has utilized google glass to refilm employee training videos in a first person view management trainees also wear google glass during rush hour periods and review the footage for constructive visual feedback capriottis uses an appbased loyalty program referencesedit  a b john grossmann january   using smartphones and apps to enhance loyalty programs the new york times retrieved february     franchise chatter exclusive qa interview with ashley morris ceo of capriotti’s retrieved april     a b c d capriottis sandwich shop inc retrieved    a b samara kalk derby  capriottis sandwiches stand out amid competitors the capital times  wisconsin state journal   a b c ethan rothstein  capriotti’s sandwich shop coming to rosslyn retrieved    a b c capriotti’s sandwich shop celebrates th restaurant retrieved    a b lauren jow  las vegasbased sandwich shop opens at the market place the orange county register   jill henebry january  talking turkey  capriottis branches out delaware business review   a b lindsay friedman june   franchise of the day to stand out from its competitors this sandwich shop has an extra tasty nightly ritual entrepreneur retrieved august     a b tovin lapan  capriottis bobbie collects yet another accolade encyclopedia of sandwiches author tells usa today that shops turkey sub is among her favorites las vegas sun   tim oreiley  heroes welcome well not as envisioned las vegas business press   a b c d tracy stapp herold  no ordinary hero retrieved    a b c tracy stapp herold  no ordinary hero retrieved    steven r thompson  capriotti’s plans growth dallas business journal   hannah fry  capriottis sandwich shops to invade orange county the orange county register   ryan saxton popular first state sandwich shop moving into bethany retrieved    capriottis named world series of poker sandwich sponsor  retrieved    capriottis unwrapped on food network  retrieved    marketplace capriottis sandwich shop  retrieved    josh lederman  joe biden welcomes delawareborn sandwich shop to dc comes up short when trying to pay the bill retrieved    a b vice president joe biden visits capriotti’s january  retrieved    capriottis opens with free sandwiches a visit from joe biden  retrieved   