shington state wisconsin and washington dc in  it ranked  in entrepreneurs franchise  in  capriottis was ranked  in entrepreneurs franchise  productsedit capriottis specializes in cold grilled and vegetarian submarine sandwiches each restaurant roasts whole turkeys for  hours nightly hand pulls meats and makes their own meatballs and coleslaw in november  the bobbie one of capriottis signature sandwiches was voted the greatest sandwich in america by aolcom the sandwich is made with pulled turkey cranberry sauce stuffing and mayonnaise the margolets named it after their aunt in  usa today named capriottis one of the  great places for a surprising sandwich technologyedit capriotti has utilized google glass to refilm employee training videos in a first person view management trainees also wear google glass during rush hour periods and review the footage for constructive visual feedback capriottis uses an appbased loyalty program referencesedit  a b john grossmann january   using smartphones and apps to enhance loyalty programs the new york times retrieved february     franchise chatter exclusive qa interview with ashley morris ceo of capriotti’s retrieved april     a b c d capriottis sandwich shop inc retrieved    a b samara kalk derby  capriottis sandwiches stand out amid competitors the capital times  wisconsin state journal   a b c ethan rothstein  capriotti’s sandwich shop coming to rosslyn retrieved    a b c capriotti’s sandwich shop celebrates th restaurant retrieved    a b lauren jow  las vegasbased sandwich shop opens at the market place the orange county register   jill henebry january  talking turkey  capriottis branches out delaware business review   a b lindsay friedman june   franchise of the day to stand out from its competitors this sandwich shop has an extra tasty nightly ritual entrepreneur retrieved august     a b tovin lapan  capriottis bobbie collects yet another accolade encyclopedia of sandwiches author tells usa today that shops turkey sub is amo